snippet.title: Adventure | Stand-up Comedy by Ravi Gupta
snippet.description:
When life gives you lemons, sell them and go to the mountains.
You’ll come back with beautiful memories and a sore body.

This is a story about a trek I did with my friend.
I spend a lot of time in the mountains. There’s no place more peaceful.
But the moment I have to walk on uneven ground, everything changes. My body starts questioning my soul.
It’s tough, annoying, and sometimes painful.
But once I’m back home, all that’s left is a funny story—and now, that story will stay with all of us forever.

Hope you enjoyed the video.
Please like, comment & share it.

I’m also performing my stand-up comedy special in the UK and touring across India and internationally!
Tickets for all my shows are live here: https://linktr.ee/Shudhdesicomic

Follow me on Instagram: 
@shudhdesicomic - https://www.instagram.com/shudhdesicomic

#raviguptacomedy #standupcomedy  #indianstandupcomedy  #comedy  #comedyvideo

snippet.title: Jaat Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Jaat Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma. Jaat Featuring Sunny Deol vs Randeep Hooda in a Mass Masala Action Thriller based on a Layered Storytelling inspired from Mythology History of Raavan & his end by a Single Warrior! 

Jaat Full Movie Story Outline & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Can Sunny Deol repeat Gadar 2 Success or Bollywood Formula with South Director prove unlucky just like Sikandar? Find out now!

Jaat is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film written and directed by Gopichand Malineni (in his Hindi debut), and produced by Mythri Movie Makers and People Media Factory.The film stars Sunny Deol in lead role alongside Randeep Hooda, Vineet Kumar Singh, Regina Cassandra, Saiyami Kher, Ramya Krishnan, Jagapathi Babu and others in supporting roles. The film score and soundtrack is composed by Thaman S.

Principal photography commenced in June 2024 and was extensively filmed across Hyderabad, Bapatla and Visakhapatnam.

Jaat was theatrically released on 10 April 2025.

MS Dhoni returns as CSK captain for IPL 2025 after Gaikwad injury blow
MS Dhoni will captain CSK for the remainder of IPL 2025 after Ruturaj Gaikwad was ruled out of the tournament with an elbow fracture. Head Coach Stephen Fleming confirmed the development on Thursday (April 10), the eve of the team's home game against Kolkata Knight Riders.
Gaikwad, 28, sustained a blow to his elbow while facing Tushar Deshpande in CSK's clash against Rajasthan Royals on March 30. Though he featured in the next two games, against Delhi Capitals and Punjab Kings, scans have now confirmed a fracture.
"Unfortunately, Ruturaj Gaikwad is going to be ruled out of the tournament," Fleming said. "He got hit in Guwahati. He's been operating with an amount of pain. We got an X-ray, which was inconclusive, and we had an MRI, which revealed a fracture in his elbow, so we're disappointed and feel for him.
"We appreciate the efforts that he's gone to in terms of trying to play but unfortunately, he'll be out of this tournament for now. We have an uncapped player in MS Dhoni who will take over as captain for the remainder of the IPL."
The injury is a major setback for the five-time winners, who have lost four of their first five matches and sit ninth in the standings. With Gaikwad out, they lose a key figure in an already misfiring top order. Notably, he also has been CSK's leading run-scorer in three of the last four seasons.

Good Bad Ugly is an Upcoming 2025 Latest Movie Starring Ajith Kumar, Trisha Krishnan & Others. Written & Directed by Adhik Ravichandran. Produced by Naveen Yerneni & Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers Banner. Music Composed by GV Prakash Kumar.

In Cinemas from April 10th, 2025.

snippet.title: एक विधवा जूते नहीं पहन सकती - Prem Rog Movie Scene - Padmini Kolhapure - Rishi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Movie : Prem Rog - A Tale of Love, Heartbreak, and Resilience (1982)
Director: Raj Kapoor
Cast: 

Rishi Kapoor as Devdhar "Dev," a penniless-but-educated orphan raised by his maternal uncle
Padmini Kolhapure as Manorama "Rama" Singh, the daughter of the local aristocratic family
Shammi Kapoor as Bade Raja Thakur, Rama's paternal uncle
Nanda as Chhoti Maa, Rama's mother
Tanuja as Raj Rani, wife of Raja Virendra Pratap Singh
Sushma Seth as Badi Maa, wife of Bade Raja
Kulbhushan Kharbanda as Virendra "Vir" Singh, Rama's father
Raza Murad as Raja Virendra Pratap Singh Narendra's elder brother
Om Prakash as Panditji, the priest; Dev's maternal uncle
Dulari as Panditji's wife
Vijayendra Ghatge as Kunwar Narendra Pratap Singh, Rama's ex husband
Bindu as Chamiya

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4368: Mannu Se Mulaqat
--------------------------------------------------------
Bapuji breaks free after being stuck at home and hurries to see his childhood friend one last time before he leaves for America. Will he make it?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4368 | 10 Apr 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090476644

snippet.title: Jaat Interview | Sunny Deol Vs Sunny Leone जैसे सवाल- Sunny Deol, Randeep Hooda के जवाब | जाट Movie
snippet.description:
हमारे साथ जुड़ें इस खास इंटरव्यू में जहां हम बात कर रहे हैं बहुचर्चित फिल्म "जाट" की। यह फिल्म सनी देओल और रणदीप हुड्डा की प्रमुख भूमिकाओं के साथ दिखेगी और तेलुगू निर्देशक गोपीचंद मलिनेनी की हिंदी डेब्यू भी है। 10 अप्रैल, 2025 को रिलीज़ होने वाली इस फिल्म में रेजिना कैसेंड्रा, सैयामी खेर और विनीत कुमार सिंह भी नज़र आएंगे।

इस इंटरव्यू में, सनी देओल और रणदीप हुड्डा मजेदार तरीके से सनी देओल vs सनी लियोनी जैसी तुलना पर प्रतिक्रिया देते हैं और जाट के किरदार निभाने के अपने अनुभव साझा करते हैं। पर्दे के पीछे की झलक, मजेदार पल और इस फिल्म को खास बनाने वाली बातों पर गहराई से नजर डालिए। सनी देओल और रणदीप हुड्डा के बेबाक जवाब और "जाट" का एक्सक्लूसिव कंटेंट मिस न करें!

Join us as we dive into an exclusive interview about the highly anticipated movie Jaat. Starring Sunny Deol and Randeep Hooda, this film marks Telugu director Gopichand Mallineni's Hindi debut. Set to release on April 10, 2025, Jaat also features Regina Cassandra, Saiyami Kher, and Vineet Kumar Singh. In this interview, the stars respond to intriguing comparisons such as Sunny Deol vs. Sunny Leone, and share their thoughts on portraying Jat characters. Get ready for behind-the-scenes insights, hilarious moments, and a deeper look into what makes this film a must-watch. Don't miss Sunny Deol and Randeep Hooda's candid responses and exclusive content from Jaat!

Welcome to Suraj Kumar Review! In this video, we're diving into the gritty and action-packed Jaat, starring the powerhouse Sunny Deol and the intense Randeep Hooda. Set against the raw backdrop of rural Haryana, this film promises to deliver high-voltage drama, explosive action, and powerful performances. But does it live up to the hype? Let's find out!

Sunny Deol's explosive comeback and his signature action sequences

snippet.title: तूम चाहो तो मुझे अपना मान सकती हो - जेठ जी के हाथ लगी बेबस औरत - Prem Rog Movie Scene
snippet.description:
Movie : Prem Rog - A Tale of Love, Heartbreak, and Resilience (1982)
Director: Raj Kapoor
Cast: 

Rishi Kapoor as Devdhar "Dev," a penniless-but-educated orphan raised by his maternal uncle
Padmini Kolhapure as Manorama "Rama" Singh, the daughter of the local aristocratic family
Shammi Kapoor as Bade Raja Thakur, Rama's paternal uncle
Nanda as Chhoti Maa, Rama's mother
Tanuja as Raj Rani, wife of Raja Virendra Pratap Singh
Sushma Seth as Badi Maa, wife of Bade Raja
Kulbhushan Kharbanda as Virendra "Vir" Singh, Rama's father
Raza Murad as Raja Virendra Pratap Singh Narendra's elder brother
Om Prakash as Panditji, the priest; Dev's maternal uncle
Dulari as Panditji's wife
Vijayendra Ghatge as Kunwar Narendra Pratap Singh, Rama's ex husband
Bindu as Chamiya

snippet.title: #Video | लाइसेंसी | Licensee | Neelkamal Singh ft. Akanksha Puri | New Bhojpuri Song | भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
भोजपुरी का असली स्वैग लौट आया है! नीलकमल सिंह की दमदार आवाज़ और आकांक्षा पुरी की शानदार अदाओं के साथ पेश है लेटेस्ट धमाका "लाइसेंसी" — देखिए और सुनिए सिर्फ़ @SaregamaHumBhojpuri पर! 💥🎶

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song Name : Licensee
Hindi - लाइसेंसी
Singer - Neelkamal Singh
Feat - Akanksha Puri
Music - Vinay Vinayak
Lyrics - Ashutosh Tiwari
Director - Paddy And Mukesh Mishra 
Choreographer - Vishnu Kumar 
Dop - Chiranjeevi 
Editor - ASY Films
Di - Rohit Singh
Arranged & Programming-Vinay Vinayak 
Mix & Master - beenuV@V2studio
Recordist - Brajesh Bagi

Lyrics:-

मुखड़ा 
हमरे जमाना चले , आगे पीछे थाना चले 
करीले इशारा तबे , सारा शामियाना चले 
बड़ी लागत डरेस तोर फैंसी बाटे 
रात बितावे साथ में चल$ 2 हाथ में बाटे करेंशी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 
जनता के दरबार लागेला , कार के बाटे एजेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 

अंतरा 1 
तहार जवानी सुना ए रानी खतरा में बा 
बिलन से मिलन लिखल करेजा पतारा में बा 
   कातना लेबु त बोला मान जयबु 
   असली मरद पहचान जयबु 
   हो साझही के नाचत तू बिहान जयबु 
   पावते ही खुला उल्हा फान जयबु 
लागिला ठोके केहू ना रोके, आवे जे इमरजेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 

अंतरा 2 
सुना ए कली रायफल के नली , तहरे प बा 
तोहार खजाना हमार निशाना, नजरें प बा 
    नखरा करे में गोली चली जाई 
    सारा माहौल ई बदल जाई 
    ग़दरल जवानी तोहार गल जाई 
   कोरा लेके जब नीलकमल जाई 
लेबेला माजा ऑफर बा आजा , खाली बाटे भकेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 
रात बितावे साथ में चल$ 2 हाथ में बाटे करेंशी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे

इस ट्रैक को सभी ओटीटी प्लेटफॉर्म्स पर सुनें।

YouTube Music - https://music.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_lwcQCG6SeGphBaAw6E6azuzB19I0WXYrc
Apple Music - https://itunes.apple.com/album/id/1803627947
JioSaavn - https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/licensee/pQO,leiiWpM_
Gaana - https://gaana.com/album/licensee
Amazon Music - https://music.amazon.in/albums/B0F221MNPW

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: 40 दिन गर्मी में सुबह-सुबह इसे खाकर देखिये कैसी भी कमजोरी,थकान-सुस्ती रहेगी दूर तंदुरस्ती मिले भरपूर
snippet.description:
#summerrecipebyeatyammiecious 
#energybooster #kheer 

40 दिन गर्मी में सुबह-सुबह इसे खाकर देखिये कैसी भी कमजोरी,थकान-सुस्ती रहेगी दूर तंदुरस्ती मिले भरपूर
Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*INGREDIENTS required :-

1/3cup - Broken Barley
700ml - Low Fat Milk
1-2tbs - Poppy Seeds
10-12 soaked - Almond
1/3cup - Rock Sugar
1/2cup - Dry Coconut
1 cup - Lotus Seeds
1-2 - Cinnamon Stick
1/2ts - Green Cardamom Powder
2ts - Clarified Butter
(If you want extra healthy sweetness you can also add jaggery or jaggery powder, sugar free substitute instead of mishri as well)

Today I will tell you a very easy way to make Daliya kheer in which we will use barley Daliya, which is jau ka daliya. It is easily available in the market and you should eat its barley especially in summers because it is a grain which has a cold effect and it cools your body from inside and it has a lot of health benefits. You can also give it in the diet of diabetes patients because barley is also considered good for their diet. Then you can easily make it for children, adults and for yourself. In the video, I have told its very easy method, but in this way barley kheer is made. It becomes very tasty. In this, if you eat a bowl of Daliya kheer in the morning, you will get a lot of health benefits and by continuously taking it in your diet, whatever nutritional deficiency you have will be fulfilled.  You can see in the video how I have first washed the daliya with water. It is very important to do this. Then after that we have to fry it well in a little ghee and then after adding water to it, we have to cook it in the cooker by putting the whistle on so that the daliya becomes soft quickly and after that, however many bowls of milk you want to make for breakfast, we just have to add that many bowls of milk and cook it because the daliya gets cooked well after the whistle of the cooker and after adding milk, we just have to cook it for 5 to 10 minutes. Then I have especially added cinnamon to it and then I have added almonds and poppy seeds to it. 
 Due to which the nutritional value of this Daliya kheer also increases and then we have to grind it and add it in it and after this I have also grated some dry coconut in it so that it feels good when it comes in the mouth while eating and it also has many health benefits. Then I have added sugar candy in it to sweeten this kheer. If you want, you can also add sugar and if you want, you can also add jaggery powder or a substitute. If you make this kheer for a diabetic patient. Then we have added roasted makhana and a little cardamom powder in it and very easily our Jaag Daliya kheer is ready. If you include it in your diet, you will remain healthy, so if you like this recipe of mine, then please do not forget to like the video at all.....✌️

localized.title: 40 दिन गर्मी में सुबह-सुबह इसे खाकर देखिये कैसी भी कमजोरी,थकान-सुस्ती रहेगी दूर तंदुरस्ती मिले भरपूर
localized.description:
#summerrecipebyeatyammiecious 
#energybooster #kheer 

40 दिन गर्मी में सुबह-सुबह इसे खाकर देखिये कैसी भी कमजोरी,थकान-सुस्ती रहेगी दूर तंदुरस्ती मिले भरपूर
Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*INGREDIENTS required :-

1/3cup - Broken Barley
700ml - Low Fat Milk
1-2tbs - Poppy Seeds
10-12 soaked - Almond
1/3cup - Rock Sugar
1/2cup - Dry Coconut
1 cup - Lotus Seeds
1-2 - Cinnamon Stick
1/2ts - Green Cardamom Powder
2ts - Clarified Butter
(If you want extra healthy sweetness you can also add jaggery or jaggery powder, sugar free substitute instead of mishri as well)

Today I will tell you a very easy way to make Daliya kheer in which we will use barley Daliya, which is jau ka daliya. It is easily available in the market and you should eat its barley especially in summers because it is a grain which has a cold effect and it cools your body from inside and it has a lot of health benefits. You can also give it in the diet of diabetes patients because barley is also considered good for their diet. Then you can easily make it for children, adults and for yourself. In the video, I have told its very easy method, but in this way barley kheer is made. It becomes very tasty. In this, if you eat a bowl of Daliya kheer in the morning, you will get a lot of health benefits and by continuously taking it in your diet, whatever nutritional deficiency you have will be fulfilled.  You can see in the video how I have first washed the daliya with water. It is very important to do this. Then after that we have to fry it well in a little ghee and then after adding water to it, we have to cook it in the cooker by putting the whistle on so that the daliya becomes soft quickly and after that, however many bowls of milk you want to make for breakfast, we just have to add that many bowls of milk and cook it because the daliya gets cooked well after the whistle of the cooker and after adding milk, we just have to cook it for 5 to 10 minutes. Then I have especially added cinnamon to it and then I have added almonds and poppy seeds to it. 
 Due to which the nutritional value of this Daliya kheer also increases and then we have to grind it and add it in it and after this I have also grated some dry coconut in it so that it feels good when it comes in the mouth while eating and it also has many health benefits. Then I have added sugar candy in it to sweeten this kheer. If you want, you can also add sugar and if you want, you can also add jaggery powder or a substitute. If you make this kheer for a diabetic patient. Then we have added roasted makhana and a little cardamom powder in it and very easily our Jaag Daliya kheer is ready. If you include it in your diet, you will remain healthy, so if you like this recipe of mine, then please do not forget to like the video at all.....✌️

            Don't forget to follow these steps:)

snippet.title: மொறு மொறு உளுந்து வடை & வேர்கடலை சட்னி | Medu Vada & Peanut Chutney | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Urad dal Vadai  
Kumbakonam's culinary gold! Imagine the aroma of freshly fried vadais and the vibrant flavors of homemade chutney. Chef Deena takes us on a culinary journey to Kumbakonam, where he meets Mr. Sakthi Krishnan of Shree Vinayaga Catering Services, a master of traditional South Indian cooking. Prepare to be inspired as they share the secrets behind their irresistible Medhu Vadai and Peanut Chutney.  The intricate techniques and regional nuances that make these dishes truly exceptional are elaborated in this video

Recipe by Mr. Sakthi Krishnan - 94431 61929
Sri Vinayaka Catering Service.
No 67, Bakthapuri Street, Kumbakonam.
Landmark : Near by Court Rounding, Next to V.K Thirumana mandapam .

Medhuvada
Urad Dal - 1/4 Kg
Green Chilli - 2 Nos.
Chopped Ginger - 2 Tbsp 
Chopped Carrot - 2 Tbsp
Rice Flour - As Required 
Coriander Leaves - Few Springs 
Curry Leaves - Few Strings 
Pepper - 1 Tsp
Asafoetida - 1 Tsp
Salt - To Taste
Oil - For Fry

Peanut Chutney

Peanuts - 100g
Ginger - As Required 
Garlic - 2 Cloves
Dry Red Chilli - 3 Nos. 
Grated Coconut - 50g 
Tamarind - A Small 
Piece Salt - To Taste
Shallots - For Tempering 
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Curry Leaves - For Tempering 
Oil - For Tempering


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

#chef #food #cooking #vada

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4366 - Kaise Khulega Darwaza!| Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku
